             was indicted for <rs id="t18300218-117-off643" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300218-117-off643" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300218-117-off643" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300218-117-cd644" type="crimeDate">18th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300218-117-off643 t18300218-117-cd644"></join>, 1 pair of trousers, value 4s.; 1 waistcoat, value 4s.; 1 shirt, value 3s., and 1 towel, value 3d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300218-117-victim774" type="victimName">
                     Simon 
                     Maryon
                  <interp inst="t18300218-117-victim774" type="surname" value="Maryon"></interp>
